{"tid":703811,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"到底VR可唔可以應用喺家畜/寵物","createTime":"2018-06-16T02:46:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T07:03:43.000Z","uid":12421,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0a09c8bc0df25f3ccee2b11642da8bc7ae627141","tid":703811,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:46:35.000Z","msg":"若果應用到喺動物上 以後就算用細啲嘅空間飼養 佢哋都可以好開心咁發育 最後turn out就係可以用少啲嘅土地資源 去培養差唔多質素嘅肉質（因為聽講啲豬牛羊放牧會開心啲 肉質會好啲） 結果因為成本下降而價格下跌<br />\n<br />\n而放喺寵物到 可以用嚟訓練導盲犬/海豚之類有一定訓練空間需要嘅動物 其妙處不言而喻<br />\n<br />\n定係已經有技術做緊而樣嘢？係的話希望巴打可以糾正我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3089e47f4b7d6f06083df011c2e01cbf31c3e19","tid":703811,"uid":29914,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:50:49.000Z","msg":"聽落好殘忍下。"},{"pid":"04239633f2e19ba81cbaa212a9ec194292727b48","tid":703811,"uid":1255,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:53:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黑鏡"},{"pid":"b0a0b86812ac903f850c636cfa2757f2f626c1d9","tid":703811,"uid":1067,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:59:01.000Z","msg":"養港豬ok"},{"pid":"916db63d75f0b1af04f35ed77ffa4723da478beb","tid":703811,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"04239633f2e19ba81cbaa212a9ec194292727b48","tid":703811,"uid":1255,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:53:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黑鏡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T03:03:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5461d0c066f4167fdef7b68d42230d53665c4040","tid":703811,"uid":76105,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T03:07:11.000Z","msg":"若果應用到喺<span style=\"colo